le？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40661585_Evidence_of_predatory_behavior_by_carnivorous_dinosaurs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F40661585_Evidence_of_predatory_behavior_by_carnivorous_dinosaurs&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=c8d2927a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40661585_Evidence_of_predatory_behavior_by_carnivorous_dinosaurs</a><br />\n<br />\n熊貓曾經係肉食性，佢哋嘅消化系統可以處理肉喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.unimelb.edu.au/sciencecommunication/2013/10/05/do-pandas-eat-meat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.unimelb.edu.au%2Fsciencecommunication%2F2013%2F10%2F05%2Fdo-pandas-eat-meat%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=32d46587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.unimelb.edu.au/sciencecommunication/2013/10/05/do-pandas-eat-meat/</a><br />\n<br />\n你點知冇留下化石？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"因為形成化石的條件好嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n你要迅速埋起成條屍，唔好比其他動物食，然後仲唔可以腐爛，直接礦物化。在自然界中，呢個唔似係常見事件。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"Fossils are formed in different ways, but most are formed when a plant or animal dies in a watery environment and is buried in mud and silt. <span class=\"xx-large\">Soft tissues quickly decompose leaving the hard bones or shells behind. </span>Over time sediment builds over the top and hardens into rock. It is when the processes of erosion occur that these secrets in stone are revealed to us.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://australian.museum/learn/australia-over-time/fossils/how-are-fossils-formed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faustralian.museum%2Flearn%2Faustralia-over-time%2Ffossils%2Fhow-are-fossils-formed%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=3ba66382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://australian.museum/learn/australia-over-time/fossils/how-are-fossils-